{
  "prompt": "A minimalist black and white logo design featuring two stylized 'M's creatively intertwined, forming a sleek, modern emblem. The logo includes a handwritten signature-style text that says 'Mark Manthy' underneath the emblem, giving it a personal, bespoke touch. The design is clean and professional, with the emblem centered above the signature. The background is white, and the overall style is elegant and timeless.",
