{
  "prompt": "A refined, artistic logo featuring an intertwined 'M' and 'C' monogram, representing the creative collaboration between Mark Manthy and Clara Elowen Greenfield. The logo should be sleek and modern, combining serif and handwritten elements. The 'M' is bold and grounded, while the 'C' is elegant and flowing, symbolizing balance and duality. Below the monogram, the text reads 'Mark & Clara' in a minimalist serif font. The color scheme is black and soft gold on a warm off-white background, evoking sophistication, emotion, and creative power.",
